      <title>摩根士丹利称债券多头在指数进入前加大对印度的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/bond-bulls-lift-india-bets-pre-index-entry-morgan-stanley-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利表示，追踪摩根大通新兴市场债券指数的投资者已为印度的纳入做好了准备，截至 5 月底，其资产的 3.6% 配置在了印度主权债务上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/bond-bulls-lift-india-bets-pre-index-entry-morgan-stanley-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 04:41:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年加密货币经历最糟糕的一周后，比特币延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/bitcoin-btc-extends-drop-after-one-of-crypto-s-worst-weeks-of-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经历了 2024 年第二大周跌幅之后，加密货币市场的损失正在不断增加，这反映出对比特币交易所交易基金的需求降温以及货币政策的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/bitcoin-btc-extends-drop-after-one-of-crypto-s-worst-weeks-of-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 04:06:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>下一任印尼领导人表示将对支出协议保持克制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/prabowo-budgets-4-3-billion-for-free-meals-to-keep-deficit-cap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼候任总统普拉博沃·苏比安托与即将离任的政府达成协议，为学校免费膳食计划拨款 71 万亿卢比（43 亿美元），此举不会超出预算赤字上限，并旨在缓解市场对扩张性支出的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/prabowo-budgets-4-3-billion-for-free-meals-to-keep-deficit-cap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 03:55:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国家债务风险加剧，印尼债券成为亚洲受创最严重债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/indonesia-s-bonds-hit-hardest-in-asia-as-state-debt-risks-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去两周，由于人们对印尼债务的担忧加剧，印尼国有电力公司的美元债券成为亚洲跌幅最大的债券。这给当地借款人带来了压力，他们面临 60 亿美元的债务到期日，预计到 2025 年底。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/indonesia-s-bonds-hit-hardest-in-asia-as-state-debt-risks-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
